ZH: 这个坡很陡，要小心走。  
EN: This slope is very steep, be careful when walking.

ZH: 车子在陡坡上停住了。  
EN: The car stopped on the steep slope.

ZH: 我们决定爬上山坡。  
EN: We decided to climb up the hillside.

ZH: 这个坡坡很长，要跑得快。  
EN: This slope is very long, you have to run fast.

ZH: 雨后的山坡湿滑危险。  
EN: The hillside after rain is slippery and dangerous.

ZH: 他在山坡上玩得很开心。  
EN: He had a lot of fun playing on the hillside.

ZH: 这个城市建在陡坡上。  
EN: This city is built on a steep slope.

ZH: 老人小心在山坡上走。  
EN: The old man walks carefully on the hillside.

ZH: 我们在山坡上找到了一处很好的野营地点。  
EN: We found a great camping spot on the hillside.

ZH: 地震导致山坡滑坡。  
EN: The earthquake caused landslides on the hillside.

